    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for a Class II CPB device with Medium model influence. Validation evidence demonstrates RHI predictions within 15% of bench measurements across all 5 operating points. The relative hemolysis index at worst-case conditions satisfies RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Uncertainty quantification has been declared for the overall assessment; sensitivity analysis scope is under review for a subsequent revision. The credibility evidence is sufficient to support the intended regulatory submission.",
